  "title": "Two round metallic UFOs spotted in Sobradinho [2000]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/14/two-round-metallic-ufos-spotted-in-sobradinho-2000/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-sf",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUNE 11th, 2000</strong>. Time: 17h00 pm. Duration: 10 minutes. Two witnesses at the Polo de Cinema, in Sobradinho, Distrito Federal, observed two round metallic UFOs, flying slowly at an altitude &#8220;higher than airplanes&#8221; as one of the witnesses described. The shiny UFOs were seen in favorable visibility and climatic conditions moving towards the North direction without leaving traces of condensation. No film or photographs of the event were reported.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.578. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no Polo de Cinema em Sobradinho, Distrito Federal”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>JUNE 11th, 2000. Time: 17h00 pm. Duration: 10 minutes. Two witnesses at the Polo de Cinema, in Sobradinho, Distrito Federal, observed two round metallic UFOs, flying slowly at an altitude &#8220;higher than airplanes&#8221; as one of the witnesses described. The shiny UFOs were seen in favorable visibility and climatic conditions moving towards the North direction [&hellip;]</p>\n",
